<div id="fb_tab">
<div id="fb_tab_l">On...Goto</div>
<div id="fb_tab_r">&nbsp;<img src="images/fblogo_mini.gif" /></div> 
</div> 
<div id="fb_pg_wrapper">
<div id="fb_pg_body">
	Saut (bas&eacute; sur une expression) vers une ligne avec une &eacute;tiquette<br \>
<br \>
<div class="fb_sect_title">Syntaxe</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<b>On</b> <i>expression</i> <b>Goto</b> label1[, ...]<br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Description</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
Branchement vers diff&eacute;rents labels d&eacute;pendant de la valeur de <i>expression</i>. Une valeur de l'expression de 1 effectuera un branchement vers la premi&egrave;re &eacute;tiquette, une valeur de 2 vers la seconde, etc.  Si la valeur de <i>expression</i> est z&eacute;ro (0) ou plus grande que le nombre d'&eacute;l&eacute;ments dans la liste, l'ex&eacute;cution se poursuit sur la d&eacute;claration qui suit imm&eacute;diatement <tt><b>On...Goto</b></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
Il est recommand&eacute; d'utiliser l'instruction conditionnelle et structur&eacute;e <tt><a href="KeyPgSelectcase.html">Select Case</a></tt> &agrave; la place de <tt><b>On...Goto</b></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Example</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="key">Dim</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">choice</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Integer</span><br />
<br />
<span class="key">Input</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"Enter&nbsp;a&nbsp;number:&nbsp;"</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">choice</span><br />
<br />
<span class="key">On</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">choice</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Goto</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">labela</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">labelb</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">labelc</span><br />
<br />
<span class="wrd">labela</span><span class="oth">:</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"choice&nbsp;a"</span><br />
<span class="key">End</span><br />
<br />
<span class="wrd">labelb</span><span class="oth">:</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"choice&nbsp;b"</span><br />
<span class="key">End</span><br />
<br />
<span class="wrd">labelc</span><span class="oth">:</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"choice&nbsp;c"</span><br />
<span class="key">End</span><br />
</div></tt><br />
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences avec QB</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> FreeBASIC ne g&eacute;n&egrave;re pas d'erreur de fonctionnement si <tt><i>expression</i></tt> est n&eacute;gative ou sup&eacute;rieure &agrave; 255.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Voir aussi</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
